    "Sentiment and emotion analysis techniques.",
    "Sentiment analysis is an NLP technique to capture the positive, negative, or neutral attitude from a text such as a review of a product.",
    "Sentiment analysis is important in the analysis of public opinion related to certain topics in social media (Behera et al., 2021; Suhendra et al., 2022).",
    "Emotion recognition in text documents can be performed using NLP techniques.",
    "People convey different emotions to give responses and reactions according to different circumstances."
